    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has clearly been well-cared for by its previous owners. The engine starts up reliably and runs smoothly, while the transmission provides consistent, predictable shifts. Inside, the upholstery is clean and free of major stains or tears, though you will find some light wear consistent with regular use. The exterior paint still holds a nice shine, although there are a few minor surface scratches and small stone chips upon close inspection. Overall, it is a solid, dependable car that is ready for its next owner without needing immediate repairs.",
