    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exceptional vehicle, currently preserved in impeccable showroom condition. This unit has been maintained to the highest possible standards, exhibiting no discernible wear and reflecting a level of care rarely seen on the secondary market. For the discerning buyer seeking a pristine, turn-key investment, this vehicle offers an uncompromising combination of aesthetic elegance and mechanical integrity.",
